National Mail Voter Registration Form | U.S. Election Assistance Commission
description: The National Mail Voter Registration Form can be used to register U.S. citizens to vote, to update registration information due to a change of name, make a change of address or to register with a political party.

title: Poll Worker Resources for Voters | U.S. Election Assistance Commission
description: The EAC encourages those interested in becoming poll workers at the polls on Election Day to learn more about what is required and how to sign up to work with your local election office.
